::KitKat::

She smiled at Drillbit. She kissed his cheek. "That will have to wait 
untill we get to the knew base. Now go get ready."

She walked off the bridge and went to the lab.
GoldenEye and DarkMouse were getting the CR's and the lab ready to 
move.
"Good work you too. Now as soon as you two are ready, we'll leave."

KitKat went to her room and activated the clones. She gave the 
Megatron clone the orders and he went after the Real Megatron.  It 
would follow his instructions now.  The kitkat clone walked into her 
room. She gave it the order and it left the base, heading towards 
Destructor's location, with the message that the rest of the group 
would be there shortly.
